    Scope and Contents
Student project compiled by Lynda Thompson for a tutorial with Gary Combs, includes; a catalog of the Illinois State Museum 1973 exhibit, "Art of the 1930's";  an audio tape of an interview with Robert Evans of the Art Department of the Illinois State Museum with Lynda Thompson as interviewer; selected slides of various projects done  during the New Deal Art Years, including a detailed listing; a catalog of an art exhibit at Southern Illinois University entitled "WPA revisited";  a reference list of other publications or published information on New Deal Art projects; and a research paper entitled "The New Deal Art Projects: An Integration of Administrative and Artistic Ideas"  by Lynda Thompson.  
  
